/-- **T205-d ADJ-CORR step 4'**: peterssonInner_iUnion ↔ petN bridge.

For CuspForms F, G with the standard AE-disjoint / null-measurable / integrable
hypotheses on the SL-tile UNION `⋃_q (mapGL ℝ q.out⁻¹) • fd`,
